    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see why the \"tough bacteria\" would even be an issue if the symptoms are completely gone. it feels like a lot of theoretical stuff vs how i actually feel. if i decide to just stop now and i don't get sick again, does that mean it wasn't actually a problem? like if my body handled it, wouldn't that be fine?",
